doctype html
html
  head
    base(href="/")
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0")
    meta(http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible", content="ie-edge")
    meta(name="keywords", content="scaffold typescript ts vue")
    meta(name="description", content="A basic project structure built with Vue & TS.")
    title Vue TS Arch

  body
    #weixin(style={ display: 'none' })
      img(src=require("./images/weixin.c.jpg"), width="300", height="300")

    #app
      #error-site-header

      #browser-warning
        div(lang="zh-CN")
          h2 网站正在加载中，请稍候&hellip;&hellip;
          p 如您长时间看到本页面，也许是因为网络状况不稳定，请尝试刷新页面。也有可能是您的浏览器年代有点久远或过于个性，超出了本网站能够支持的范围之外，请尝试将系统的 IE 升级到 10.0 以上版本，或直接使用
            a(href="https://www.mozilla.org/zh-CN/firefox/new/") 火狐
            | 、
            a(href="https://www.google.cn/chrome/browser/desktop/index.html?standalone=1") 酷容
            | 、或各大极速版浏览器。
          p 温馨提示：您也可以使用手机访问本站 ;)

        div(lang="en-US")
          h2 Website is now LOADING&hellip;&hellip;
          p
            | If this page has been shown for a minute,
            | maybe it's because your network condition isn't quite good.
            | Please try to refresh it.
          p
            | Another possible cause is that your browser is aged or quite uncommon,
            | which beyonds the supporting scope of this site.
            | In this case, please upgrade your Internet Explorer to at least v10.0,
            | or use #[a(href="https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/new/") Firefox]
            |  / #[a(href="https://www.google.com/chrome/browser/desktop/index.html?standalone=1") Chrome].
          p Kindly remind: you can also use your cellphone to visit ;)

    script(type="text/javascript").
      function showWarning() {
        var warningElem = document.getElementById('browser-warning')
        if (warningElem == null) { return }
        warningElem.className = 'show'
      }
      setTimeout('showWarning()', 3000)

    noscript
      #no-script-warning
        p(lang="zh-CN") 您的浏览器似乎禁止了 JavaScript 脚本。
          | 而本网站与许多现代化网站一样需要 JavaScript 才能正常工作 :(
        p(lang="en-US") Your browser seems to disable JavaScript.
          | This website (just like many other modern websites) needs JavaScript to properly work :(
